# thoroughfare

**Instance Property**

The street name at the place.

## Declaration

```swift
thoroughfare?: string;
```

## Discussion

For example, one possible [doc://com.apple.mapkitjs/documentation/MapKitJS/Place/thoroughfare] in Golden Gate Park in San Francisco, California, is `"John F Kennedy Dr"`.

## Street address

- **subThoroughfare**: The number on the street at the place.
- **fullThoroughfare**: A combination of thoroughfare and subthoroughfare.
- **postCode**: The postal code of the place.
